quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  24,21,"Ko onon …ďen gom…óin…ďe, wata on jokku …óate Seytaane …óen, kala jokku…óo …óate Seytaane …óen, pellet, o yamiray [mo] ko boni kon e ko a√Īaa kon. Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden; hay e gooto e moo…óon laa…ďataano poomaa, kono Alla hiMo la…ď…ďina on mo O Muuyi. Alla ko O Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  24,22,"Wata joomiraa…ďe …ďural ngal e yaajeende nden e moo…óon woondu wonndema …ďe okkortaa …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen e …ďillii…ďe …ďen e feru…ďe …ďen ka Laawol Alla, yo …ďe yaafo. Kaa on yi…óaa yo Alla yawtan on? Alla ko O Yawtoowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,23,"Pellet, …ďen wonu…ďe tukkude [sonnaa…ďe] saŇčii…ďe welsindii…ďe gom…óin…ďe, …ďe hu…óaama ka aduna e ka Laakara no woodani …ďe Lepte maw…óe"
  24,24,"√Ďalnde seedoytoo e dow ma…ď…ďe …óen…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, ko …ďe laatinoo kon hi…ďe golla"
  24,25,"Nden √Ďalnde Alla huu…ďinanay …ďe [njo…ďdi] Diina ma…ď…ďe Goongaha kan, …ďe annda pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga ∆Āannguka kan"
  24,26,"Rew…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii wor…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen. Wor…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii rew…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen. Rew…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii wor…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen, wor…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii rew…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen. ∆Āee …óoo ko hisnaa…ďe e kon ko …ďe wowlata, no woodani …ďe haforaneede e arsike teddu…óo"
  24,27,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe, wata on naatu e cuu…ói tanaa cuu…ói mo'on …óin haa duŇčino…óon salminon e dow yim…ďe majji …ďen, ko …óum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on. Bela jo'o onon on waajitoto"
